  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK274">
<l>tavamaṟain tallavai ceytal putaṉmaṟaintu</l>
<l>vēṭṭuvaṉ puṭcimiḻt taṟṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He who hides himself under the mask of an ascetic and commits sins, like a sportsman who conceals himself in the thicket to catch birds.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
